quote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>膊真係要慢慢feel 先feel到<br />\n<br />\n利申 55kg 上到70 但仲好廢</blockquote><br />\n師兄幾高？</blockquote><br />\n178</blockquote><br />\n有咩上磅心得share</blockquote><br />\n一星期操5-7日<br />\n其實我操得唔耐 每日一部位 每部位5個動作  <br />\n但堅操1個鐘<br />\n仲有飲on serious mass</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nserious mass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要食野方面 唔可以有肚餓感 一日差唔多4-5餐 <br />\n另加操"},{"pid":"53772277c9702b80d980dea0e45513bbd0bcedac","tid":168222,"uid":23326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:11:06.000Z","msg":"操膊食到應一應 痛到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe3b60771e75f97618de7fea9a701705fcdd5b4","tid":168222,"uid":88767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>借po 我想問下做gym體重係咪會升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做左兩星期gym 都係慢跑30分鐘 之後負重<br />\n點知愈來愈重 但食野同之前一樣喎<br />\n好撚灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做 gym就係為左增重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔要肥絲大隻 我來減磅架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e8965b183f50477cdf018aa08a2db7e8659665","tid":168222,"uid":89155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[quote<br />\n你自己有冇圖先 我練膊都有少少心得</blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以分享下你點FEEL</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以！<br />\n我share我個routine<br />\n<br />\narnold press 前面數字係重量<br />\n30 warm up x 12<br />\n40 x 8<br />\n50 x 6<br />\n60 x 6<br />\n70 x 6<br />\n75 x 6 即刻再做 30x12<br />\n<br />\n較斜張bench 大約45度或者高少少<br />\n心口貼bench飛後膊<br />\n做4組 每組15下<br />\n<br />\n之後普通坐係度飛膊<br />\n10x15<br />\n20x10 drop 10x10<br />\n25x10 drop 20x10 drop 10x10<br />\n35x8 drop 25x10 drop 20x10 drop 10x10<br />\n<br />\n飛前膊，玩法同飛橫膊一樣<br />\n<br />\n之後再推膊 是但揀個動作 可推機或overhead press<br />\n重量每組加<br />\n<br />\n之後飛後膊（可用fly機/做facepull)<br />\n重量每組加<br />\n<br />\n之後飛橫膊superset前膊<br />\n用餅飛 Range of motion唔洗多<br />\n淨係做上到頂 落少少就再上<br />\n<br />\n大約係咁 想知再講"}]}